            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="text-primary coolfactor">No Confusion</h3>
                    <p class="featurefont">
                        Never feel in the dark about how or where the numbers came from. Every screen in ZapLeaf has an explanation <button class="btn btn-link coolfactor" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#helpModal"><i class="fa fa-question-circle fa-lg"></i></button> button for help and a reference that relates back to the Michigan Child Support Formula. You will always know the how and why for each number.
