<div class="modal fade" id="helpModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="helpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true"></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="helpModalLabel">Sample Help</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p><strong>2013 MCSF-S 2.08(B)</strong>: Calculate the premium deduction by dividing the premium by the number of individuals covered (including the parent) and multiply by the number of qualifying additional children covered.</p>
                <p><strong>2013 MCSF-S 3.05(A)(1)</strong>: Determine each parent’s monthly health care premium attributable to the children by dividing the premium by the number of individuals covered (including the parent) and multiply by the number of children covered in this case.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>